lines.line:
Mark: Oh, come on!{nl}
What're we supposed to do{nl}
against a walking corpse?!

Ayase: Um... hehe!{wait}{nl}
You fellas are so dreamy~!{nl}
Ayase's all a-flutter!{fffb}{fff7}So? Let me off the hook~ hmm?

Takeda: Lord Kandori, stand back!{fffb}{fff7}Listen up!{wait}{nl}
Don't let a single one{nl}
make it out alive!

Reiji: ...You'd kill me?{wait}{wait}{wait}{nl}
How amusing...{wait}{wait}{wait}{nl}
You're the one who dies!

Demon: Ia! Shub-Niggurath, ia!{nl}
Yog-Sothoth!!{wait}{wait}{nl}
Ia ia ia ia aaaaaah!

Nanjo: First a robot,{nl}
now a stuffed doll?{wait}{nl}
I'd rather not, but needs must!

Hariti: My child...{wait}{wait}{nl}
sweet Maki...{wait}{wait}{nl}
give my Maki baaack!!

Mark: H-Hey!{wait}{nl}
Isn't that seriously{nl}
Sonomura's mom?

Maki: If what Nanjo said{nl}
is true...{fffb}{fff7}there's still time!{wait}{nl}
Stop this madness{wait}{nl}
and bring the world back!

Kandori: Heh...{wait}{nl}
You'd preach nonsense to a god...{wait}{nl}
Such folly is itself a sin.{fffb}{fff7}A god always judges and condemns.{wait}I've no ears for the words of insects.

Nanjo: Kandori...{wait}{wait}{wait}{nl}
we'll bring the curtain down{nl}
on this farce!{wait}{nl}
If that's what you wish!

Ayase: Ahahaha...{wait}{nl}
S-Sorry, Yokouchi.{wait}{nl}
Bit late to apologize now, huh?

Nemesis: Oh-hohohoho!{wait}This is my true form!{fffb}{fff7}Beauuutiful!!{wait}{nl}
And so{nl}
eleeegant!!

Yukino: ......{wait}{nl}
Keep the jokes to your face!!{wait}{nl}
That's too generous!!{fffb}{fff7}I'm too stunned for words.

Ayase: Hey now,{nl}
have you ever looked in a mirror?{wait}{nl}
Totally different!

Nemesis: Kiiiiii!!{wait}{nl}
Silence! Silence! Silence!{fffb}{fff7}That smart-mouthed look{nl}
of yours{nl}
I'll carve right off!!

Thanatos: Trans-for-ma-tion{nl}
complete!!{wait}{nl}
Here comes Yuriko!{fffb}{fff7}Now, everyone,{nl}
I'll wipe you out!{wait}{nl}
Be ready for it!
